data.description: Welcome to 175 Calverton Ln in the highly sought after River Crest community! This exquisite home offers a perfect blend of elegance, functionality, and community amenities. Step inside and be greeted by a formal dining room, ideal for hosting gatherings and creating lasting memories. Adjacent is a versatile office/study, providing a quiet space for work or relaxation. The heart of this home is the open kitchen, featuring quartz countertops, engineered hardwood floors, and stainless-steel appliances including a cooktop, wall oven, and microwave. A walk-in pantry and an additional counter area, perfect for your coffee bar, ensure convenience and efficiency in your culinary endeavors. Upstairs, you'll find four bedrooms, including a luxurious master suite with a spa-like ensuite bathroom. Three additional bedrooms and two full bathrooms provide ample space for family and guests. The River Crest community offers an array of amenities, including a large swimming pool, tennis courts, clubhouse, playground, and fishing ponds. Plus, enjoy the convenience of being just minutes away from Trilith, Piedmont Fayette, and Peachtree City. Don't miss the opportunity to make 175 Calverton Ln your dream home in a vibrant and welcoming community. Schedule your showing today and experience luxury living at its finest!
